Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.71,Normal,Moka,0,0,0,,Không! Thả tôi ra! Thả tôi ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.53,Normal,Moka,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
